      • addTypeAdapter

        public MultiAutoComplete.Builder addTypeAdapter(@NonNull
                                                AutoCompleteTypeAdapter<?> typeAdapter)
        Add a AutoCompleteTypeAdapter to the MultiAutoComplete being built. The type adapter must be built with one of the AutoCompleteTypeAdapter.Build factory methods.

        Note: the insertion order will determine which type adapter will handle a specific token. If there are multiple adapters that support a specific token format, only the first matching will be used.

        Parameters:
        typeAdapter - The type adapter to add.
        Returns:
        The builder for chaining calls.
